sql:
SELECT simulations.sim_name, simulations.owner_id, results.eta_Cl_simulated
FROM simulations
INNER JOIN results ON simulations.sim_id = results.sim_id;

SELECT split_name
FROM splits
WHERE split_id = 1 AND split_type = 'Custom';

SELECT simulations.sim_name, users.user_name
FROM simulations
JOIN users ON simulations.owner_id = users.user_id;

SELECT sim_name 
FROM simulations
WHERE status = "active" AND owner_id = 0;

external_knowledge:
- "travelers" refers to users;
- "digital realm" signifies the system or platform in question;
- "frequented more than a handful of times" translates to accessing the system more than five times;
- "voyage details" include user ID, name, email, role, creation and last update timestamps, and last login timestamp;
- "harbored their digital torch" means whether they are active users (is_active).
